## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **omalizumab Xolair 2003** = first FDA anti-IgE moderate-severe persistent allergic asthma. IgE Cε3 결합 → FcεRI 결합 차단. quantum-VQE 의 IgE Cε3 pocket modeling 첫 fit. asthma 의 biologic era 시작.
2. **mepolizumab Nucala 2015 + reslizumab Cinqair 2016 + benralizumab Fasenra 2017** = anti-IL-5 / IL-5Rα triple — severe eosinophilic. benralizumab 가 IL-5Rα ADCC-enhanced afucosylated. quantum-VQE 의 IL-5 / IL-5Rα cytokine-receptor pocket fit.
3. **dupilumab Dupixent 2018** = first FDA IL-4Rα severe T2 asthma → 2024 6+ pediatric asthma → 2024 COPD eosinophilic. atopic march cross-disease (AD + asthma + EoE + CRSwNP + prurigo nodularis + COPD). quantum-VQE 의 IL-4Rα paradigm.
4. **tezepelumab Tezspire 2021** = first FDA anti-TSLP severe asthma — paradigm 만성 phenotype-agnostic. T2-low + neutrophilic 까지 effective (other biologics 불가). quantum-VQE 의 TSLP-TSLPR-IL7Rα ternary complex modeling.
5. **SMART (single maintenance and reliever therapy) GINA 2019+** = budesonide+formoterol 만성 표준 — SABA monotherapy 비추천 paradigm shift. ICS-formoterol 가 maintenance + rescue 통합.
6. **Trelegy Ellipta 2020 asthma** = first FDA asthma triple inhaler (ICS+LABA+LAMA fluticasone+umeclidinium+vilanterol). 2017 COPD 후 asthma 확장. severe asthma add-on alternative to biologic.
7. **itepekimab + astegolimab + IL-33 axis (research)** = next biologic frontier. IL-33-ST2 alarmin 가 TSLP 와 동등한 upstream. quantum-VQE 의 IL-33 + ST2 pocket modeling.
8. **depemokimab (Phase 3) long-acting IL-5 6-monthly** = mepolizumab 4주 → 26주 dosing 변환. compliance 향상 + treatment burden 감소. anti-IL-5 selectivity + half-life engineering quantum-VQE fit.
9. **bronchial thermoplasty (BT) 2010** = device-based refractory severe asthma — airway smooth muscle radiofrequency ablation. biologic era 후 niche 한정.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, asthma 임상 의미 한정. inhaled formulation pulmonary deposition + airway epithelium PK 미시뮬.

